snippet.title: No Fear - YULTRON  Kellin Quinn  Amber Liu (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
No Fear - YULTRON  Kellin Quinn  Amber Liu (Lyrics)
--

#YULTRON  Kellin Quinn  Amber Liu #No Fear
This video is purely fan-made, if you (owners) want to remove this video, please CONTACT US DIRECTLY before doing anything.
We will respectfully remove it.
--
"No Fear"
- YULTRON  Kellin Quinn  Amber Liu -

Fall asleep just for today
I heard you say
We don’t need to do anything
The world outside is cold and grey
Said it looks like rain
Let’s stay in bed we’ll watch
The world just wash away

It’s you and me against the world
Just you and me against the world
But we won’t fall
No, we stand tall
It’s you and me against the world
Just you and me against the world
But have no fear
Cause I’m right here
So have no fear
Cause I’m right here

(Against the world, against the world)
(So have no fear cause I’m right here)
(Against the world, against the world)
(So have no fear cause I’m right hеre)

Cities getting loud
And wе can drown out every sound
Don’t wanna feel haste
So do it our way
With every trace
We can’t hear what they say
Sun don’t shine the way that it used to
Clouds still gray, but we’re safe in this room
Can I fall asleep laying with you next to me
There’s no place I’d rather be

It’s you and me against the world
Just you and me against the world
And I don’t mind
Just wasting time
It’s you and me against the world
Just you and me against the world
But have no fear
Cuz I’m right here
So have no fear
Cuz I’m right here
(don’t care cuz life ain’t fair)

(Against the world, against the world)
(So have no fear cause I’m right here)
(Against the world, against the world)
(So have no fear cause I’m right here)
